---
name: feedback_form
resource: Customization
resource_owner: anyone
configuration:
  properties:
    rate:
      validation:
        presence: true
    message:
      validation: { presence: false }
---

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-12 col-xl-6">
    <p>This page is showcasing basic CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) pattern using AJAX and <a href="https://documentation.platform-os.com/reference/custom-model-types/custom-model-types" target="blank">customization</a>.</p>
    <p>Data will be saved/updated/deleted using native <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/API/Fetch_API" target="_blank" rel="noopener">fetch</a>.
    If you need support for legacy browsers, take a look at excellent <a href="http://polyfill.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">polyfill service</a>.</p>
    <p>Data retrieval will be done using <a href="https://documentation.platform-os.com/get-started/pages/pages" target="_blank">Liquid page</a> (in <a href="https://documentation.platform-os.com/get-started/pages/pages#formats" target="_blank">JSON format</a>), returning results obtained by GraphQL.</p>

    <p>Errors are logged using <code>console.log()</code>, so keep your dev tools open. You will find additional debug info in javascript console to make more obvious whats happening in the javascript.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="col-12 col-xl-6">
    <div class="card">
      <div class="card-header">Simple console log</div>
      <div class="card-body" style="max-height: 150px; overflow-y: auto;">
        <ul id="logger"></ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-5">
  <div class="col-12">
    <h2 id="read_example">[R]ead</h2>
    {% include 'feedback/read' %}
  </div>
</div>

<div class="row mt-5">
  <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-4 mt-3">
    <h2 id="create_example">[C]reate</h2>
    {% include 'feedback/create' %}
  </div>
  <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-5 mt-3">
    <h2 id="update_example">[U]pdate</h2>
    {% include 'feedback/update' %}
  </div>
  <div class="col-12 col-lg-6 col-xl-3 mt-3">
    <h2 id="delete_example">[D]elete</h2>
    {% include 'feedback/delete' %}
  </div>
</div>
